This container contains the Hystrix dashboard, an optional component in a Netflix service infrastructure

Running the dashboard
=====================

1) Start the container:

cd dockerfiles/hystrix-dashboard/
./startHystrixDashboard.sh

2) Point your browser to http://10.10.10.30:8080/hystrix-dashboard

3) In the front page of the dashboard application, enter the URL of the Hystrix stream exposed by the RSS application: http://10.10.10.30:9090/hystrix.stream
